tafsir[1]{c,v,t}:
  16,30,"Wi'anee ɓen hulirɓe Joomi maɓɓe ɗoftagol yamirooje Makko ɗen woɗɗitoo e haɗaaɗi Makko ɗin: Ko honɗum Joomi mon jippini e Annabaajo mon on Muhammadu (yo o his)? Ɓe jaaboo: Ko moƴƴere mawnde Alla jippini e makko. Hino woodani ɓen moƴƴimɓe rewugol Alla ngol ɓe moƴƴini huuwondiral maɓɓe ngal e tagu Makko ngun aduna ɗoo mbarjaari labaandi: wano ballal e yaajireede arsike. Ko ko Alla marani ɓe kon e mbarjaari ka laakara ɓuri moƴƴude diini ndin ndi O yaccinani ɓe ka aduna. Saare laakara nden moƴƴanii hulirɓe Joomi mun ɗoftagol yamirooje Makko ɗen woɗɗitoo haɗaaɗi Makko ɗin."